{
  "keyword": "CHGOBJD",
  "description": "Change Object Description (CHGOBJD)",
  "parameters": [
    {
      "name": "OBJ",
      "description": "Object",
      "help": "Object (OBJ)\n\nSpecifies the object whose description is to be changed. If qualifier 2 is not specified, *LIBL is searched to find the specified object. A library name can be specified for qualifier 2 to ensure that the correct object is changed.\n\nNote: To change the object description for objects of type *DEVD, you should first use the Allocate Object (ALCOBJ) command to obtain an *EXCLRD lock state on the device description. If this is not done, a CPF2114 message is sent, which indicates that the device description is locked. The ALCOBJ command does not have to be used if you are already signed on the display device for which the description is to be changed.\n\nThis is a required parameter.\n\nQualifier 1: Object\n\nQualifier 2: Library\n\nAlthough the following Qxxx libraries are provided by IBM, they typically contain user data that changes frequently. Therefore, these libraries are considered user libraries and are also searched:",
      "inputType": "group",
      "required": true,
      "groupKind": "qualified",
      "children": [
        {
          "name": "LIB",
          "description": "Library",
          "help": "指定できる特殊値: *LIBL, *USRLIBL, *CURLIB, *ALL, *ALLUSR",
          "inputType": "text",
          "required": false,
          "defaultValue": "*LIBL",
          "attributes": {
            "characterSet": "upper",
            "maxLength": 10
          },
          "placeholder": "*LIBL"
        },
        {
          "name": "OBJ",
          "description": "Object",
          "help": "指定できる特殊値: *ALL",
          "inputType": "text",
          "required": true,
          "attributes": {
            "characterSet": "upper",
            "maxLength": 10
          },
          "placeholder": "OBJ"
        }
      ],
      "positional": 1,
      "basic": true
    },
